    <mj-section>
      <mj-column width="100%">
        <mj-text padding-bottom="0px">
          <h2 style="font-weight: bold">People</h2>
          <p><a href="https://sneak.berlin/20200220/discord-is-not-an-acceptable-choice-for-free-software-projects/">Jeffrey Paul: Discord Is Not An Acceptable Choice For Free Software Projects</a><br />
            An argument against Discord for use with open source and public interest projects. The privacy and censorship point of view is one I appreciate but, a lot of the arguments could be made about a lot of communication systems in use today, not only Discord (namely IRC and Slack).</p>

          <p><a href="https://siliconangle.com/2020/02/19/doj-backs-oracle-google-long-running-copyright-dispute/">DOJ backs Oracle over Google in long-running copyright dispute</a><br />
            Anytime the US Department of Justice gets behind Oracle, it&rsquo;s a sign of dark times for us all. The <a href="https://spectrum.ieee.org/tech-talk/computing/software/google-v-oracle-explained-supreme-court-news-apis-software">IEEE has an overview of the Google v. Oracle case</a> and its implications if you&rsquo;re not up to speed. This could change the course of history.</p>

          <p><a href="https://jvns.ca/blog/compensation-questions/">Questions you can ask about compensation</a><br />
            Next time salary comes up in a job interview, ask them to answer some questions‚Å¶from Julia Evans&rsquo; list. It will help you understand a lot about the company as well as how you'll extract more money for yourself from the value you create for the organization.</p>

          <p><a href="https://hbr.org/2020/02/stop-calling-it-innovation">Stop Calling It &ldquo;Innovation&rdquo;</a><br />
            &ldquo;When engaging internally with employees, Danfoss, a global manufacturing company, has branded its innovation process around the simple, manageable word &lsquo;idea.&rsquo; While not everyone think they can be innovative, nearly everyone has at least one idea.&rdquo;</p>

          <p><a href="https://www.reuters.com/article/us-usa-defense-breach-idUSKBN20E27A">U.S. agency that handles Trump&rsquo;s secure communication suffered data breach</a><br />
            Having done an enormous amount of work with DISA in the past, I&rsquo;m patiently waiting for my copy of <a href="https://devopsish.com/images/disa-pii-breach.jpg">this letter</a> and the next round of free, US government-issued credit monitoring service.</p>
        </mj-text>
      </mj-column>
